01:31:33.293 --> 01:31:35.252
He was now answering
to a higher calling.

01:31:36.213 --> 01:31:39.590
It was time to go to a place
beyond tradition,

01:31:39.591 --> 01:31:42.259
to a place of buried lies...

01:31:42.260 --> 01:31:45.179
and unearthed truths.

01:31:46.723 --> 01:31:50.226
A revolution had begun within Luke's soul.

01:31:50.227 --> 01:31:54.813
He had a purpose and a calling
that went beyond any scoreboard.

01:32:10.955 --> 01:32:14.499
- What?
- It's kind of a putter.

01:32:54.497 --> 01:32:58.165
