01:32:58.166 --> 01:33:01.002
and stroked the putt of his life.

01:33:11.513 --> 01:33:16.309
Utopia is defined as a place
of mythical perfection,

01:33:16.310 --> 01:33:18.728
but I knew differently.

01:33:18.729 --> 01:33:21.897
Utopia is indeed real.

01:33:21.898 --> 01:33:25.818
It's a place where the voice
of truth resides...

01:33:25.819 --> 01:33:30.155
and eternal trophies line the shelves.

01:33:30.156 --> 01:33:33.199
A place where there are no accidents.

01:33:35.411 --> 01:33:39.497
I guess you're asking yourselves
whether or not he made the putt.

01:33:40.124 --> 01:33:42.459
The better question is,

01:33:42.460 --> 01:33:44.878
